<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 09:11:03 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>韩国称朝鲜已向俄罗斯运送6,700个集装箱弹药</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/north-korea-has-sent-6700-containers-munitions-russia-south-korea-says-2024-02-27/</link><description>韩国媒体周二援引国防部长的话称，自 7 月以来，朝鲜已向俄罗斯运送了约 6,700 个集装箱，载有数百万弹药，以支持其对乌克兰的战争，这表明朝鲜正在进行武器转让。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 08:37:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/north-korea-has-sent-6700-containers-munitions-russia-south-korea-says-2024-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>阿里巴巴旗下南亚电商巨头Daraz在备忘录中宣布裁员</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/alibabas-south-asian-e-commerce-giant-daraz-announces-layoffs-memo-2024-02-27/</link><description>阿里巴巴旗下的电子商务平台 Daraz Group 代理首席执行官 James Dong 周二在路透社看到的一份致员工的内部备忘录中表示，该公司已宣布在整个集团进行裁员，以“采用更加精简和灵活的结构”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 06:49:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/alibabas-south-asian-e-commerce-giant-daraz-announces-layoffs-memo-2024-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>随着中国出货量激增，印度四月至一月钢铁进口量创六年新高</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/indias-apr-jan-steel-imports-six-year-high-china-shipments-surge-2024-02-27/</link><description>路透社周二看到的临时政府数据显示，在中国出货量的带动下，印度钢铁进口量在截至3月份的本财年前10个月触及六年来新高，并且印度是成品钢材的净进口国。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 06:43:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/indias-apr-jan-steel-imports-six-year-high-china-shipments-surge-2024-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>澳大利亚贸易部长表示，中国葡萄酒争端可能在几周内得到解决</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/china-wine-dispute-may-be-resolved-weeks-australian-trade-minister-says-2024-02-27/</link><description>澳大利亚贸易部长唐·法雷尔周二表示，与中国有关澳大利亚葡萄酒关税的贸易争端可能“在几周内”得到解决，从而消除了限制其对华出口的最后障碍之一。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 06:11:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/china-wine-dispute-may-be-resolved-weeks-australian-trade-minister-says-2024-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>越南计划进行工会改革以避免贸易困境，但冒着外国公司不安的风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/vietnam-plans-union-reform-avert-trade-woes-risking-foreign-firms-unease-2024-02-27/</link><description>联合国官员和外交官表示，共产党统治下的越南预计将在今年批准联合国自由建立工会公约，此举旨在降低贸易争端风险，但可能会让一些外国公司感到不安。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 04:04:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/vietnam-plans-union-reform-avert-trade-woes-risking-foreign-firms-unease-2024-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国商飞将在东南亚5国展示C919、ARJ21飞机</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/chinas-comac-showcase-c919-arj21-jets-5-southeast-asian-countries-2024-02-27/</link><description>中国国有飞机制造商中国商飞公司周二表示，将在五个东南亚国家进行C919和ARJ21喷气式飞机的飞行展示​​，为未来的国际销售奠定基础。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 03:52:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/chinas-comac-showcase-c919-arj21-jets-5-southeast-asian-countries-2024-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>独家：渣打银行暂停中国客户新的离岸渠道投资</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/stanchart-suspends-new-investments-clients-via-chinas-outbound-channel-2024-02-27/</link><description>渣打银行表示，由于当地市场和货币疲软，海外投资需求激增，该行已暂停中国客户通过配额渠道对离岸产品进行新投资。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 02:21:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/stanchart-suspends-new-investments-clients-via-chinas-outbound-channel-2024-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>日本股市飙升让投资者远离陷入困境的中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/soaring-japanese-equities-offer-investors-cozy-distance-troubled-china-2024-02-27/</link><description>随着经济和地缘政治困境促使投资者大量逃离中国，许多人将资金转移到日本，这给基准日经指数带来了额外的提振，使其飙升至历史新高。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 02:04:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/soaring-japanese-equities-offer-investors-cozy-distance-troubled-china-2024-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>日本通胀高于预期，亚洲股市波动，交易员保持警惕</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-02-27/</link><description>亚洲股市周二下跌，日本通胀略高于预期，令投资者在本周欧洲和美国公布价格数据之前保持警惕，但有迹象表明机构买家正在围观，比特币延续涨势。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 01:59:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>台湾称5艘中国海警船进入前线岛屿附近海域</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-minister-says-5-china-coast-guard-ships-entered-waters-around-kinmen-2024-02-27/</link><description>台湾一位部长周二表示，在与北京的紧张关系持续升级之际，五艘中国海警船周一进入台湾前线金门岛周围的禁区或限制水域，但在被警告离开后不久就离开了。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 01:23:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-minister-says-5-china-coast-guard-ships-entered-waters-around-kinmen-2024-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>关键数据公布前美元下跌，比特币飙升至 57,000 美元以上</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-droops-key-us-data-looms-yen-firms-cpi-beat-2024-02-27/</link><description>周二美元走势不利，因为市场期待一周的美国经济数据，这些数据将提供有关美联储可能多久开始降息的新信号。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 01:20:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-droops-key-us-data-looms-yen-firms-cpi-beat-2024-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>夏威夷邻国基里巴斯发现中国警察后美国发出警告</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-cautions-after-hawaii-neighbor-kiribati-gets-chinese-police-2024-02-27/</link><description>在路透社报道中国警察正在夏威夷邻国基里巴斯偏远环礁国家工作后，美国周一警告太平洋岛国不要接受中国安全部队的援助。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 01:19:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-cautions-after-hawaii-neighbor-kiribati-gets-chinese-police-2024-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国房地产危机刺激需求，重组专家增加香港员工</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/restructuring-specialists-boost-hong-kong-staff-china-property-crisis-stokes-2024-02-26/</link><description>随着中国的房地产危机导致债务重组交易激增，全球重组专家 Alvarez &amp;amp; Marsal 和 Houlihan Lokey 增加了在香港的员工数量，使其成为香港金融业招聘中罕见的亮点。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 23:28:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/restructuring-specialists-boost-hong-kong-staff-china-property-crisis-stokes-2024-02-26/</guid></item><item><title>巴西BRF结束七连败，扭亏为盈</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/brazils-brf-ends-seven-quarter-losing-streak-earns-16526-million-q4-2024-02-26/</link><description>根据周一的财报，巴西家禽和猪肉加工商 BRF SA 在 2023 年最后三个月实现利润 8.23 亿雷亚尔（1.6526 亿美元），结束了连续七个季度的亏损。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 23:02:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/brazils-brf-ends-seven-quarter-losing-streak-earns-16526-million-q4-2024-02-26/</guid></item><item><title>美国参议院委员会就中国药明康德和华大基因法案举行听证会</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/us-senate-panel-sets-hearing-chinas-wuxi-apptec-bgi-bill-2024-02-26/</link><description>美国参议院一个委员会周一表示，将于 3 月 6 日就一项法案举行听证会，该法案将禁止联邦机构与中国华大基因、药明康德和其他受关注的生物技术公司签订合同。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 22:59:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/us-senate-panel-sets-hearing-chinas-wuxi-apptec-bgi-bill-2024-02-26/</guid></item></channel></rss>